- **`SortableList.razor`** — renders each item via `ItemTemplate` with Move Up/Down buttons (disabled at boundaries).
- **`SortableList.razor.cs`** — code-behind with generic `TItem`. Copies `Items` into an internal `_items` list on each parameter set, so the parent's collection is never mutated. After a swap, it fires `OnOrderChanged` with a read-only copy.

